Toomes. your family's here!

2124
02:05:59.135 --> 02:06:01.137
[Mu]

2125
02:12:33.821 --> 02:12:36.657
Hi. I'm captain america.
here to talk to you...

2126
02:12:36.824 --> 02:12:40.786
About one of the most valuable traits
a soldier or student can have.

2127
02:12:40.953 --> 02:12:42.621
Patience.

2128
02:12:42.788 --> 02:12:44.915
Sometimes Patience is the key to victory.

2129
02:12:45.082 --> 02:12:47.126
Sometimes it leads to very little...

2130
02:12:47.293 --> 02:12:49.628
And it seems like it's not worth it.

2131
02:12:49.795 --> 02:12:51.297
And you wonder...

2132
